{"tid":2243892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發時空 沈旭暉019us]特朗普 Vs 拜登 : 應對中國的真正不同在哪裏?","createTime":"2020-10-15T05:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T06:10:27.000Z","uid":378282,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8c221b80a5cf500bd1ffcd396ae134d91f8b33","tid":2243892,"uid":378282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JEMNm1u_6mA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJEMNm1u_6mA&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=4fc43e2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JEMNm1u_6mA</a><br />\n<br />\n很多人認為，中美脫鉤已成定局，特朗普和拜登上台，都沒有分別。然而，關鍵並非立場，而是手法。拜登的手法則是在現有機制下，盡力和中國周旋，卻忽視了「現有機制」包括種種民主制度、西方法治、國際組織、言論自由等文明規範，都已經被中國洞悉弱點，「適合中國國情的就用、不適合的就把它丟棄」。繼續因循，過多十年，整個人類文明範式都會被扭轉。<br />\n<br />\n⏺特朗普Vs拜登的選擇：由被港區國安法入侵的美國校園談起<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/42244898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F42244898&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=9486a2df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/42244898</a>"},{"pid":"4a7f5a4f1611c3c390146896aa7f16f61cbf8608","tid":2243892,"uid":378282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2f6ac022c2d514dacc66811646ef1cfbe61b83","tid":2243892,"uid":378282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=